<h1>Arctic Expansion</h1>

<h2>Rules</h2>
<p>Print the map double-sided. At the start of the game, the Arctic map will be on the pre-warming side. Once the Arctic Warming Command Card is played, flip the Arctic board to the post-warming side and add the additional Water Territory cards to the Water Territory deck.</p>
